translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「くくく、中々壊しがいのありそうな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Heh heh heh, quite a face that looks worth breaking"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 綺麗な顔立ちしてやがるぜ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You’ve got a pretty face, indeed."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ？　それならなんだってんだ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh? Then what the hell is it?"
"This one has the Holy Pope as their mother,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 父に魔王ランスを持つお前の弟！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and the Demon King Rance as their father—your younger brother!
"This one has the Holy Pope as their mother,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 父に魔王ランスを持つお前の妹！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and the Demon King Rance as their father—your younger sister!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そして＜エール＞は魔王ランスを
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "And <Eiru> is gathering the children of the Demon King

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 退治する為に魔王の子達を集めてるんだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: to defeat the Demon King Rance!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後は自分で言えと促され、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: who urged you to say the rest yourself,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは頷き、ランスJr.の前に出た。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You nodded and stepped forward in front of Rance Jr.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぐわぁぁーはははははははは！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gwahahaha ha ha ha ha ha ha!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 馬鹿なんじゃねぇのかお前！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Are you some kind of idiot!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だーれがテメェの言うことなんか聞くか！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Who the hell would listen to anything you say!?"
"If you can beat me, I'll consider it!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ただし負けたらお前らは俺の家来になりやがれ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But if you lose, you lot will become my servants!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「わーっ、兄弟で喧嘩なんていかんだすー！」
「わーっ、兄妹で喧嘩なんていかんだすー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Waah, brother and sister fighting is no good!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんだこいつらの強さは！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What is with the strength of these guys!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんな強い連中がいたなんて……！」
「くそっ、これだけは使いたくなかったが……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Damn, I didn’t want to use this at all, but..."
"Ah, he's drinking some kind of medicine!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「へへへ、寿命を削る代わりに……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Heh heh heh, in exchange for shortening my lifespan...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パワーが上がる薬、よお……！」
殺す殺す殺すぅぅううーーー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm gonna kill kill kill youuuu!!!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ひーーっ！　なんかヤバそうだすよー！」
「お、俺様より強い奴がいるなんてぇ……」
ランスJr.はその場に大の字にぶっ倒れた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance Jr. collapsed into a spread-eagle position right there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お前の兄貴、めちゃ乱暴な奴だな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: your big brother is a really rough guy..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ま、これで落ち着いて話を聞いてくれんじゃね？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, I guess now he'll calmly listen to what you have to say?"
"Eek! Am I going to be killed!?"
